* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 18-Mar-25 18:15 Page   1
*                                      EXERC7.CBL
* Options: LIST(EXERC7.LST) ASMLIST(EXERC7.GRP)
     1 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
     2
     3 PROGRAM-ID.    EXERC7.
     4 AUTHOR.        YHAGO PESSOA.
     5 INSTALLATION.  FATEC-SP.
     6 DATE-WRITTEN.  18/03/2025.
     7 DATE-COMPILED. 18-Mar-25 18:15.
     8 SECURITY.     APENAS O AUTOR PODE MODIFICA-LO.
     9
    10 ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
    11
    12   CONFIGURATION SECTION.
    13     SOURCE-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    14     OBJECT-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    15     SPECIAL-NAMES.    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    16   INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
    17     FILE-CONTROL.
    18       SELECT   CADALU   ASSIGN TO DISK
    19       ORGANIZATION IS  LINE  SEQUENTIAL.
    20       SELECT   CADATU   ASSIGN TO DISK
    21       ORGANIZATION IS  LINE  SEQUENTIAL.
    22
    23 DATA DIVISION.
    24
    25   FILE SECTION.
    26     FD CADALU
    27       LABEL   RECORD    STANDARD
    28       VALUE  OF FILE-ID IS "CADALU.DAT".
    29     01 REG-ENT.
    30       02 NUMERO-ENT    PIC 9(05).
    31       02 NOME-ENT      PIC X(20).
    32       02 NOTA1-ENT     PIC 9(02)V99.
    33       02 NOTA2-ENT     PIC 9(02)V99.
    34       02 NOTA3-ENT     PIC 9(02)V99.
    35       02 NOTA4-ENT     PIC 9(02)V99.
    36       02 SEXO-ENT      PIC X(01).
    37     FD CADATU
    38       LABEL   RECORD   STANDARD
    39       VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "CADATU.DAT".
    40     01 REG-SAI.
    41       02 NUMERO-SAI    PIC 9(05).
    42       02 NOME-SAI      PIC X(20).
    43       02 MEDIA-SAI     PIC 9(02)V99.
    44       02 SEXO-SAI      PIC X(01).
    45   WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    46     77 FIM-ARQ  PIC X(03)  VALUE "NAO".
    47     77 MEDIA-C  PIC 9(02)V99.
    48
    49 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    50
    51   TESTE.
    52     PERFORM INICIO.
    53     PERFORM PRINCIPAL
    54       UNTIL FIM-ARQ EQUAL "SIM".
    55     PERFORM TERMINO
    56     STOP RUN.
    57
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 18-Mar-25 18:15 Page   2
*                                      EXERC7.CBL
    58   INICIO.
    59     OPEN INPUT  CADALU
    60          OUTPUT CADATU.
    61     PERFORM LEITURA.
    62
    63   LEITURA.
    64     READ CADALU
    65       AT END
    66       MOVE "SIM" TO FIM-ARQ.
    67
    68   PRINCIPAL.
    69     PERFORM GRAVACAO.
    70     PERFORM LEITURA.
    71
    72   GRAVACAO.
    73       COMPUTE MEDIA-C = (NOTA1-ENT + NOTA2-ENT + NOTA3-ENT
    74       + NOTA4-ENT)/4.
    75       MOVE NUMERO-ENT  TO NUMERO-SAI.
    76       MOVE NOME-ENT    TO NOME-SAI.
    77       MOVE MEDIA-C     TO MEDIA-SAI.
    78       MOVE SEXO-ENT    TO SEXO-SAI.
    79       IF SEXO-ENT = 'F'
    80         WRITE REG-SAI
    81       END-IF.
    82
    83   TERMINO.
    84     CLOSE CADALU
    85           CADATU.
